metadata.title: Bald Eagle Nests - EVOS Database

creators.name: Wildlife Service (USFWS), Alaska Department of Natural Resources

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This dataset depicts locations of known bald eagle nests. Nests were identified in the field by USFWS staff. Most of these locations identified by boat survey. GIS database produced as a result of the Exxon Valdez Oil Spill (EVOS) for Natural Resources Damage Assessment (NRDA). The intended purpose of this database is to provide a resource for use in the oil spill damage identification, oil spill response, habitat restoration activities.
